{"title":"瓜洲古渡","authors":["许少飞"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓜洲古渡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一层浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾推来唐的繁华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一扁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又载去宋的屈辱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡商渡僧渡兴渡亡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡欢渡忧渡王渡侯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人的愁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染湿了点点吴山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉了的眼里有三两星火渔舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣、腐朽、诗情、戟钩……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半都随了逝水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一半如沙如土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在此沉积、淹留"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代风吹绿了江南江北"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡轮窗口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"探出黑的非洲白的欧洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古渡头又氤氲着葱茏的诗意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江里火树银花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雨中，长江万里绿藤上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只瓜又碧绿碧绿……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}